{"about_the_game":"LEGO Brawls is an easy-pick-up, &quot;everybody-friendly&quot; platform brawler. Whether you're looking for a quick play casual battle, an unlockables grind, a competitive rank climb to the top of the global leaderboards, or even just creative brawler building, LEGO Brawls has something for you!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/Header-BuildYourOwnUniqueBrawler.jpg?t=1704236044\" /><br>Design your ultimate LEGO Minifigure hero with unique style, strategy and personality. With over 77 TRILLION combination possibilities, almost anything is possible. A cactus with an attitude? A scrappy janitor ninja who happens to have fighting chickens? A sledgehammer-swinging clown with a few scores to settle? Sure!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/legobrawls-customization.gif?t=1704236044\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/Header-PlayThroughYourFavoriteLEGOThemes.jpg?t=1704236044\" /><br>From the swashbuckling shores of Barracuda Bay, to the waterlogged caverns of Ninjago Seabound, to a dusty wild west saloon and the mythical Monkie Kid jungle, all of your favorite LEGO themes are brawlable! Collect unlockable minifigures, power-ups, and emotes along the way. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/legobrawls-gameplay.gif?t=1704236044\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/extras/Header-BrawlWithCross-Play.jpg?t=1704236044\" /><br>Cross-play your friends across platforms! Team up and brawl 4v4, party with friends, or play a battle royale-style game mode where it\u2019s \u201cevery-player-for-themself\u201d. With multiple game modes, levels have unique challenges and win conditions.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Brawler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731460/53619cff6313cc470b14758cded7efb8e96d95e1.jpg"},{"name":"Fashionista","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731460/1dc8ba4f74180db0628700326e47521f9cf8d7e8.jpg"},{"name":"Party Goer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731460/451e126c0acf47fc8f689789e9ed3ee6ff49664d.jpg"},{"name":"Top Brawler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731460/7bc1890cf87889019e0319041373705b9873fb9f.jpg"},{"name":"Mechanic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731460/0de88f6c320b1384fd4b0c1281ae5e9fae7e3ca0.jpg"},{"name":"I Like to Party","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731460/df4bfa808b225208a1fb1e59156ac022b7509e98.jpg"},{"name":"Big Time Brawler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731460/ec9b0c703d9b143e8501717d98654b0d85cf6c6b.jpg"},{"name":"Legendary Brawler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731460/d8d1ed8a36ed789541c02047ca819c4740f82c9e.jpg"},{"name":"High Five","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731460/fc658997db3604a153b9bb7c788cea52f517a712.jpg"},{"name":"Master Brawler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731460/62b58b7afd22d5a073f7bae01caf77a42101f5fb.jpg"}],"total":18},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1704236044","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/page.bg.jpg?t=1704236044","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731460/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1704236044","capsule_i